    <h1>Australia Foreign-Born Population<br>Official ABS Data<em>#1 of 20 countries at ~32%</em></h1>
    <p class="theme-hero__sub">Australia has the highest foreign-born share among 20 comparable Western countries at ~32% (ABS 2024), reflecting decades of a deliberate points-based immigration system.</p>
